# Auth conventions

- User/API types live in `src/types/auth.ts`; use snake_case on wire (FastAPI).
- OAuth uses PKCE; pending state in `sessionStorage` via `src/lib/storage.ts`.
- POST login body to `/api/v1/auth/oauth`; do not store provider secrets in the client.
- Set `VITE_AUTH_MOCK=true` for local UI tests without real OAuth apps.
